snippet.title: Amber Rose not twerking at Trinidad Carnival 2016
snippet.description:
Amber Rose came to Port of Spain, Trinidad for this year's Carnival 2016. She played with Lost Tribe. Not twerk session was had unfortunately. Black Chyna was supposed to be there but she wasn't on that truck.

I bet Wiz Khalifa is mad. He should be. Bruh, fine don't stay single long. You gotta wife for life! 

Machel Montano's "Waiting on the stage" is playing in the background. I probably heard that tune God knows how many times when I was down there. 

Trinidad 2016 was pretty dope and I will be posting more videos from what I experienced down there. Stay tuned #CARNIVAL2016
